                    <a href="/detail"><img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1579965342575-16428a7c8881?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&ixid=MnwxMjA3fDB8MHxzZWFyY2h8Nnx8cGFpbnRpbmclMjBhcnR8ZW58MHx8MHx8&auto=format&fit=crop&w=500&q=60" alt="Painting"></a>
