                <div class="featured-card">
                    <a href="/detail"><img src="https://media.istockphoto.com/photos/set-of-luxury-wicker-chairs-picture-id1169933338?b=1&k=20&m=1169933338&s=170667a&w=0&h=aIwffQFwwn0S85zmhsgWYX7GCebPFb1SAO0gobt7yG0=" alt="Furniture"></a>
